Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:26.46,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama... Wasn't that a girl's scream just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.24,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Help! Somebody, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:47.02,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, help me! Those guys suddenly attacked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:49.38,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:52.85,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.63,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We won't let you get away just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:58.08,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,The fun is just about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.90,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, you! That girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:19.11,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's a trillion years too early for scum like you to even talk to my Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.11,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,WHAT did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:26.63,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Everybody... It would be best if you all just apologized to Rance-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:27.86,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Shuddap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:33.28,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Although you are unworthy, be grateful that I'm about to give you the honor of my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:37.49,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I am the strongest hero in history:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:39.61,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:50.25,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,C... cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.75,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You weaklings should die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:04:00.31,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stabbing Rance Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.61,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.44,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,P...p...p...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.60,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.78,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I think not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:32.49,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sill, what are you waiting for?\NTake everything valuable from the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:39.77,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Erm... Well, Rance-sama... I think that would be considered desecration of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:45.57,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sill! You're my slave, so don't you dare contradict me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.99,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm sorry, Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.00,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:05:00.70,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Erm... Thank you very much...\NHow can I show my gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:07.45,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Gratitude? You can show it with your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.19,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.19,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:15.97,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama is doing it with another girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:29.72,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"The Desert Guardian"\NPart 1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.70,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So good! Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:03.75,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,More! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:24.62,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I will do whatever it takes to resurrect you... No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:31.03,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...And then you will kill all those bastards at the Oasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.79,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama! We are so glad you came, even though it's such a long way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:10.77,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah, I did come a long way... Show some more gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:15.41,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah... yes... Anyway, the master is waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.66,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I've brought Rance-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.00,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:42.50,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Welcome, Rance-sama. I'm the sheikh of this oasis. My name is Ani.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.07,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wh...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.48,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I wanna screw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.79,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama has a bad habit of talking to himself from time to ti... Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.62,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's nothing, just a little thought there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:05.24,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,More importantly... Since I am the strongest and most handsome fighter in history...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:09.32,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...You must have had a good reason to call me here, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:21.65,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes. It's those bandits that started attacking this village about three months ago,\N"Green Scorpion", that I'd like to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.90,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,...And what about those "Guri-guri suko-suko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.29,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's "Green Scorpion", Rance-sama! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:37.89,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Green Scorpion" have taken captive around twenty virgins from this village over the last three months...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.90,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?! Virgins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:40.90,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:33.97,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Many others have fallen victim to them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:35.84,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.58,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And all we know about "Green Scorpion" is that their leader is a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:42.42,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We've formed a self-defense squad and tried to oppose them, but it ended in disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:54.32,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Their combat skills are just too great... So we've nothing left than to rely on a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:55.69,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:10:02.08,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You don't have to say any further! I'll get rid of those "Guri-guri suko-suko" provincial bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:03.50,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:08.10,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,And then I'm gonna catch that girl-leader, and we'll be doing it over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.45,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, Rance-sama... You're drooling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.09,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama! You MUST kill that woman, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:13.69,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:19.13,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,In memory of all the victims she has killed, we can't forgive her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:25.08,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's a waste, but let it be that way if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:28.99,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm going to cut off that woman's head and decorate this table with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:30.76,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.70,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,It's nothing! Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.38,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,By the way, what about the reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:41.07,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,As I promised, we have those 200,000 gold pieces ready for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:45.25,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Of course, I'll take the money, but I do have another wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:49.02,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,If it's something you can get in this village, you can ask for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.15,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You mean it?! You really mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:59.96,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All right! I'll be sure to remember those words! Ha-ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:06.01,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm gonna kill those bandits like "one-two-three", and then I'm gonna do it with this Ani-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.58,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wh...What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:23.84,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He-he-he-he! Ani-chaaaan!... Didn't you say you'll do anything? He-he-he-he!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:30.27,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I can't take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:32.56,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama! You've got a nosebleed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.16,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Erm... Rance-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:35.40,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:42.87,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He-he-he! Ani! Rest aroused... Oh no, I mean... Rest assured that I'll do what I have to and wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:53.89,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.76,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hi, welcome! What's it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:15.55,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How would you like our special dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.56,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is something wrong, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.27,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How much would you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.72,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30 gold pieces, if you'd like it raw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.73,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wow! So cheap! All right then, I'll have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.26,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ok then, wait a second, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.25,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Is she going to get the room ready or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.05,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's nice! That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.67,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, Sill, you wait here, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.91,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:49.94,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:57.88,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:02.91,notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a8\b0\fs12}[translator note:  Rance asks for the price of "kimi", the Japanese word for "you".  However, "kimi" also means "egg yolk", and the waitress incorrectly assumes that is what he meant.]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:01.05,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, it's a yolk! An egg yo-lk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:05.89,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Call the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.92,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.37,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.42,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.34,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm the owner of this place, Idabashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:20.35,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You! Aren't you way too impudent for a haniwa?! I'm gonna slit you in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:22.89,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama! Please, have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:26.95,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,How the hell do you train the waitresses in this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.57,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Please, forgive me! Please, forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:33.28,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Shuddap! I'm hurt all the way down to my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:37.05,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to pay me 300 gold pieces as compensation.  Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.82,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Count it properly, will ya, Sill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.72,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:46.44,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:50.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Idabashi, I'm gonna question you about several things now, so be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:54.59,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah... How did I end up like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.18,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Did you say something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.47,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, no, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:00.83,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's right! Obedience is the best human quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.51,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,But I'm a haniwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:11.16,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nit-pick me once again, and you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.41,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.85,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well then, tell me all you know about "Green Scorpion".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:16.85,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.28,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Don't you "huh" me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.37,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Again... Tell me all you know about "Green Scorpion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:30.08,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes! "Green Scorpion" usually appear from the desert on nights with a crescent moon, attack the village, and then return to the desert once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.92,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nights with a crescent moon, you say?  Hey, Sill, what kind of moon is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.71,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Crescent moon, Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:43.55,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Lucky! The goddess of luck must really be hitting on me! Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.62,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well then, I'll get going now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:51.07,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Wait! There one more thing I'd like to hear about. Tell me what you know about the sheikh of this oasis, Ani-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:54.18,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ani-sama! She's the most caring person to everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:59.28,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That's not what I'm asking! Tell me if she has any weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:00.28,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:06.57,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,She may have agreed to the fee, but she might protest when I ask for her body.  And for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.95,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ani-sama doesn't have any weak points at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:16.32,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I feel like you're hiding something! Tell me the truth, or you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:21.81,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm not... Ani-sama was once attacked by some bandits in the middle of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:27.30,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,So? Did they stick it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:34.56,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well, frankly speaking... Yes. They were very strong, and all the people around just pretended they didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:39.56,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All right, then Ani-chan will definitely let me have it if I kill THOSE guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.31,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, they are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:46.23,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What?! Who did that?! Who interfered with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:50.89,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,They were all killed in the first attack of "Green Scorpion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:55.00,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You asshole! I can't do anything about it now, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:55.71,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:16:01.84,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Why would you tell me something this useless?! Isn't there anything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.26,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No! Noo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.40,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Somebody! Somebody, please, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.40,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.97,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Heh... That wasn't hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.75,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama, I've made some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.46,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,No, it's all right. Let's just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.16,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:46.25,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Geez, you're so slow! Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:13.85,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"Green Scorpion"! I have to tell everybody fast! Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.62,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hmmm....mmm. That was pretty good, Sill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:49.16,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:52.66,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,All right! For the third round, let's do it in this position!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:55.91,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah... Rance-sama?  Wouldn't it be better to take a little break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:19:03.00,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,There is no such word as "rest" in my huge Magnum's lexicon, Sill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:05.68,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:14.22,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.76,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Mwa-ha-ha-ha! I've been waiting for you provincial bandits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:20:01.71,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ha-ha-ha! They call me swordsman Rance, the destroyer of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:04.66,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama! You're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.20,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:17.51,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey, bandits! You should be grateful because I'm going to send you all to the other world myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:19.86,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah, Rance-sama! It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.46,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ahhh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.52,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.16,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:40.51,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:46.21,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,He-he-he-he!  Damn you, impudent bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:46.64,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:54.14,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Uaghhh! Stabbing Rance Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.54,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,These guys aren't human! They're just armor that somebody's manipulating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:17.51,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.59,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Fire Lazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.84,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You did really well, Sill!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:31.37,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ah! Rance-sama praised me... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:36.89,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.50,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Rance-sama!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:01.67,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.26,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,What's that tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:41.81,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Are you alive, Sill?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:42.64,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes, Rance-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:46.53,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Well... Now it's gotten interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.00,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,That man who came to kill me is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:07.27,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Kill him! ...And then destroy the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:32.71,Text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"To be continued..."
